| User Type                    | Characteristics                                                                          |
| ---------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Blood Bank Administrator** | Skilled in basic computer operations, responsible for managing inventory and users       |
| **Hospital Staff**           | Medical professionals with limited technical knowledge, require fast and reliable access |
| **Authorized Staff**         | Trained personnel who update donor and stock records                                     |
| **Donors**                   | General users with basic web usage knowledge                                             |
